---
title: Asian Stir-Fried Tofu & Garlic Rice with Veggies & Sriracha Aioli
description: We’re stirring and frying these soft little tofu cubes tonight in a lavish dark sauce. Bring out those garlic aromatics by cooking it into the
greens and the rice. What tofu stir-fry would be complete without a dollop of sriracha aioli to smother over everything. It’s a gold star
from us!

